  "remarks": "JSC Production Association Strela is a Russian military industry company. The company supplies weapons to the Russian Armed Forces under state defence orders. JSC Strela produces Oniks (Onyx) rockets and beam holders for Su-30. Both Oniks and Su-30 are used by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
